# Founders Square v2 — online multiplayer (Supabase Realtime)
#
# 1. Create a free project at https://supabase.com
# 2. Project Settings -> API: copy the URL and anon public key below
# 3. Copy this file to .env (web/dev) — the values are baked into the
#    mobile bundles at build time via `npm run cap:sync`.
#
# Vercel (founderssquaregame.com): Project Settings -> Environment Variables
#   VITE_SUPABASE_URL
#   VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
# Remove legacy founders-square-glow vars (NEXT_PUBLIC_COLYSEUS_URL, etc.).
#
# No database tables are required: the game uses Realtime broadcast
# channels and presence only.

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
